#  Personal Expense Tracker

A simple and elegant web application to track your daily expenses with category-wise calculations.

##  Features

-  Add expenses with description, amount, category, and date
-  Automatic category-wise calculations
-  Real-time summary (total, count, average)
-  Delete individual or all expenses
-  Responsive design for mobile and desktop
-  Beautiful gradient UI with smooth animations
-  Currency formatted in Indian Rupees (â‚¹)
-  8 expense categories with emojis

##  Quick Start

1. Open `index.html` in your web browser
2. Fill in the expense details
3. Click "Add Expense"
4. View your spending in real-time

